arStrings.szText: "Symon is dead. His search for knowledge ended in tragedy."
No! Akarat... I had some hope...
I'm so sorry. I managed to collect some of his writings. I thought you might like this - a thing to remember him by.
Thank you... Curse my foolishness. I shouldn't have let him go.
This wasn't your fault. But the man responsible - Elias - is gone.
A poor comfort to me, but it would comfort Symon. Thank you for bringing me back what was left of him.
